== Abakwasɛm ==
Sunyani yɛ kuro bi a kwaeɛ birentu  nsaase na ɛtwa ho ahyia wɔ nnfinfini wɔ anafoɔ atoeɛ fam wɔ Ghana. Kuropɔn Sunyani baabi a na wɔn a wɔn kɔ asono ahayɔ tena bia wɔ 19th century; yɛ nyaa ne din no firii  Akan kasa 'Osono'<ref>http://www.touringghana.com/regions/brongahafo_region.asp</ref> mu. wɔ mfei apem ahankron aduonu nan no mu (1924), na Abrofo Abae a na ɛdi yɛn soɔ saa mmere no yii  Sunyani sii hɔ sɛ  mansini no kuropɔn (district headquarters).<ref>http://www.touringghana.com/regions/brongahafo_region.asp</ref>Deɛ ɛdiisoɔ ne sɛ wɔn yɛɛ kwantenpɔn a ɛfiri Sunyani de bɛsi  [[Kumase|Kumasi]], Sunyani bɛyɛɛ kuro bi a na wɔn na wɔn ma yɛn nnobaeɛ bi tesɛ cocoa, kola nuts, ɛne nnuane bi te sɛ abroo ne baayerɛ.<ref name="Touring Brong Ahafo Region">[http://www.touringghana.com/regions/brongahafo_region.asp Touring Brong Ahafo Region] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120517125823/http://www.touringghana.com/regions/brongahafo_region.asp|date=17 May 2012}}</ref> Ɛbɛsi nnɛei Sunyani yɛ ɛfie de ma  [[Bono ne Ahafo Mantam|Bono ne Ahafofoɔ]] . Na ɛhɔ nso na abae asɛm dibea kɛseɛ a ɛwɔ wɔ mantam no mu .Sɛ yɛ de toto ho a ɛyɛ ketoa sene [[Kumase|Kumasi]], Sunyani ɛɛnyine ntɛmntɛm soɔ na ɛterɛterɛ ɛde kɔ saa nkuro mmienu yi so ɛyɛ Afiapre ɛne Abesim ɛne nkro afofro a ɛkeka ho. Sunyani yɛ kuro bi wɔn hwɛ anaa wɔn akura no yie na wɔn de no ni nso, ɛyɛ ɛkuro a anya nnpontuo.<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine</ref>

