=== Sika kura ===
Sunyani kurooɔn no wɔ sika kurabea ndwumakuo nkorabata  bebiree a ɛbi ne  Bank of Ghana, Ghana Commercial Bank, Barclays Bank, SG-SSB Bank, [http://www.bsic.com.gh/ OmniBank], Zenith Bank, Agricultural Development Bank of Ghana, Stanbic Bank, Ecobank Ghana and the National Investment Bank. Na  rural banks bɛyɛ sɛ nsia nso wɔ hɔ ɛne abeseabɔ akuoakuo ( credit unions ) ahodoɔ bi nso ɛne nsiakyibae ndwumakuo (Insurance Institutions) ahodoɔ a wɔn na wɔn ma wɔn sika kura ho dwumadie noara ɛwie pɛ yɔ anaa sɛ ɛdimu.<ref name="Touring Brong Ahafo Region" />

=== Nkitahodie ===
Sunyani kurpɔn no nkitahodie nfidie ahodoɔ no ara bi nso wɔ ho a ɛboa wɔn nkitaho die ndwuma ,ɛbi ne fixed telephone and fax lines, pay phones, mobile phones, internet and e-mail services. Deɛ ɛka ho bi nso ne ; postal services ɛbi ne  post office, mail services ndwumakuo bi te sɛ  EMS (Express mail service), DHL ɛne FedEx.

=== Nsrahwɛ ===
Nsrahwɛ bea ahodoɔ a ɛwɔ Sunyani yɛ abɔdeɛ nnoɔma a atwa kuro no ho ahyia . Wɔn wɔ nsroma mmiensa ahohogyebea  ( [[3 star hotels]] ) a ɛkyerɛ sɛ ahohogyebea papa akɛseɛ 

na ɛwɔ hɔ, ɛbɛ  boro dunum nɛɛmafoɔ  ahɔhogyebea ɛne afoforo a ɛyɛ papa, ɛne ahohofie nso bebiree ne adidibea ahodoɔ nso bi wɔ kuropɔn yi mu.<ref name="Touring Brong Ahafo Region" />	Deɛ ɛka kuropɔn yi nsrahwɛ bea yi bi ne  Cocoa House, ɛsoro sɔreɛ a agyeafa Sunyani [[Skyline]]. Ɛfie ahodoɔ wɔn asisi,Bono mantan mu ndwuma kuo asoeɛ ahodoɔ, ɛne beaɛ a wɔn tontoɔn ntaadeɛ pii.<ref name="Touring Brong Ahafo Region" /> Nfaso dan ahodoɔ a ɛwɔ Sunyani ɛbi ne Yesu ne Hene Asoredae kɛseɛ (Christ the King Cathedral), ɛne Asomdwie Hemaa Dae ( Queen of Peace Building), Knight of St. John House. Deɛ ɛkaho biom ne  [[Kintampo Waterfalls]] ɛne Boabeng  ndoee kronkron bea ( monkey sanctuary) a ɛwɔ  [[Fiema]], yɛ kwanwaa bi firi kuropɔn no mu.<ref name="Touring Brong Ahafo Region" />

