== Apɔmuden ==
Sunyani kurpɔn no ayaresabea mmiensa , ɛmu baako ne  Sunyani Mantan mu Ayaresabea ( Regional Hospital ), a ɛyɛ  state-of-the-art development, a wɔn bue ano wɔ mfei mpem mmienu ne mmiensa no mu (2003). Ayaresabea nkumaa nso nwɔtwe ɛne bia a wɔn gye awoɔ hwɛ apemfoɔ nso mmiensa, three [[Abawo|maternity]] homes a wɔn nso di dwuma wɔ Sunyani. Na Ayaresabea bebiree nso yɛ bɛ hunu bi nso wɔ hɔ.

== Akwantunsɛm ==
Sɛ ɛba bo akwantuo ho nsɛm nso a Sunyani wɔ ɛwiem hyen gyina bea (Sunyani Airport) a ɛyɛ afiyɔ ho wiem hyen gyina bea na wɔn bue ano  wɔ  Kutawonsa bosome no ne a ɛtoso du 6mmiensa wɔ mfei apem aha nkron aduoson nan (13 July 1974). Ɛsane ne sɛ akwan a Wien hyen to tu so mmerika no ɛnso no nti ɛntumi ɛma ɛwiem hyen adantɛm deɛ no ntumi ndi dwuma wɔ hɔ ( medium range aircraft), na ɛtumi fa akwantufoɔ firi hɔ kɔ Kumasi ne Takoradi wiem hyen gyina bea   . Sɛ badwam anaa dodoɔ akwantuo ho nsɛm nso a wɔn wɔ akwanso  akwantuo dwumadie nso a wɔn wɔ  MetroMass, VIP ɛne Taxicab anaa [[Tro tro]].<ref name="Touring Brong Ahafo Region" />

Sunyani wɔ amansan ahyen ahodoɔ a ɛdi akwantufoɔ de kɔ nkuro akɛseɛ ahodoɔ no bi mu te sɛ [[Nkran|Accra]]; [[Kumase|Kumasi]],  Mim, Ahafo ; Cape Coast, [[Sekondi-Takoradi|Takoradi]];  Tamale; [[ Tema]]; [[Но| Ho]]; Wa;  Bolgatanga;  Elubo;  Aflao, Techiman.

== Nimdeɛpɛ ==
Sunyani yɛ bea a sukuu nimdeɛpɛ nkuo pii no ara wɔ ɛwɔ Ɔman Ghana mu , ɛbi ne [[Sunyani Technical University]] akane [[Sunyani polytechnic]], [[University of Energy and Natural Resources]] a ɛwɔ [[Fiapre]] a ɛbɛn  Sunyani tete Kwame Nkrumah Abodeɛ mu Nyansapɛ ne nfidie ho nyansapɛ suapɔn-afudeɛ sukuu, [[Catholic University College of Ghana, Arts and Education]] a ɛwɔ  Fiapre and [[College of Science and Arts]], ɛne Penkwase - Law School. Akuo ahodoɔ a wɔn wɔ Satellite beaeɛ nso bi ne [[University of Cape Coast,]] ɛne [[Kwame Nkrumah University  Science and Technology]] -KNUST a ɛno na ɛhwɛ wɔn a wɔn wɔ akyire akyire adesua ne wɔn a wɔn bɛ sua adeɛ akyire no so wɔ Sunyani .

Sunyani wɔ ntoasoɔ sukuu bebiree na ɛbi ne  [[St James Seminary]] , a wɔn ka ntoasoɔ sukuu num wɔn ayɛ wɔn sɛ wɔn yɛadeɛ paa wɔ Ɔman  Ghana mu. Deɛ ɛkaho bi nso ne Sunyani Business Senior High School, Sunyani Secondary School, na ɛno twetwe asukuufoɔ noara bebiree firi Bono ne Ahafo mantan mu ɛne nkuro nkuro pii so ma wɔn ba bɛ gye sukuu nimdeɛ ne nteteɛ wɔ hɔ .Sukuu a wɔn ayi no sɛ ɔno na ɔyɛ adeɛ paa no ne (Susec) [[Senior High School]]  na wɔn na wɔn bɔ wɔn ho mmoɔden paa wɔ WASSCE nsɔhwɛ a asukuufoɔ nyinaa twerɛ no de firi mfei mpem mmienu ne du baako (2011) no mu debɛsi nnɛ.

Nfitiaseɛ sukuu ne nsano dwuma nimdeɛ suronko sukuu pii nso wɔ  Sunyani ne nkuro a atwa ho ahyia , ɛbi ne  St. Mary's; Lawrence Demonstration; Wesley's; Divine Montessori; Ridge Primary; Twene Amanfo Secondary Technical School (TASTECH); Sunyani Business Senior High School; [[Notre Dame High School (Ghana )]] ɛne  Don Bosco Vocational Technical Institute.

